<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Redstone</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">An emerging residential community located in the north east quadrant of Calgary, Redstone is represented by the Ward 3 Councilor in the Calgary City Council.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is surrounded by the Skyview Ranch community on the south, the 60 Street N.E. on the east, the Stoney Trail on the North and the Metis Trail N.E. on the west.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Redstone range from single-family detached units to townhomes and apartment condominiums that are regularly listed at an average price of around $370,000.</p>
        </div>
